To obtain an opportunity in the field of software development or web design with which I may utilize my education and experience with HTML, PHP, java, javascript, Oracle and/or SQL.

***

Gainesville State College Oakwood, GA, 2009-2012, A.S Engineering.

***

### Skills
##### Software: 
* Microsoft Office, Adobe Photoshop, After Effects, Dreamweaver, Flash, Blender,  Inkscape,  Eclipse, Dr Java, Aptana, GitHub, AutoCAD.

##### Programming: 
* C++, HTML, Java, Javascript, MySQL, Oracle, PHP, Python, XML.

##### Certifications: 
* Oracle 11g

***

### Experience
##### Georgia Gwinnett Public Library Lawrenceville, GA, October, 2014-Present, IT Intern
* Create documentation sites
* Redesign web pages as per department heads

##### Actaeon Systems Alpharetta, GA, July, 2014-Present Web Intern
* Modify look and feel of the products
* Create and update product information sites
* Tweak functionality of products to specifications
